last hospital.
Saturday 19 Sunday 20.1.18
Very quiet in hospital, no amusements of any kind, time drags awfully.
Monday 21.1.18
No food in preparation for operation "no bon" Put under anaesthetic about 10.45 had part of my left little toe cut away. Felt very queer after coming around. for rest of the day. Food awful. Given cold piece of tough meat vegetable about 1 after coming to, asked for drink of milk, none to be had was given hot water which I refused to drink with thanks. Foot very sore to-night.